page.title: 02Ashmanhaugh & Barton Turf
page.content:
06320321 ASHMANHAUGH: FARMS 6 BEESTON PARK The main A1151 Wroxham/Yarmouth road bisects this area. To the east of the road is wholly arable farming. To the west of the road is Beeston Park, heavily wooded and with a lake within the Park. Beeston St. Lawrence is in the north eastern corner of the park.
06330321 BARTON TURF: BEESTON HALL AND PARK Majority of area comprises the bulk of Beeston Park - mainly deciduous woodlands with lake and drainage stream enclosing Beeston Hall which is a minor stately home open to the public.
